headline: Keysight Introduces Next-Generation Embedded Security Testbench
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., April 09, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) announces the launch of the Next-Generation Embedded Security Testbench, a consolidated and scalable test solution designed to address the increasing complex security testing demands of modern chips and embedded devices. This new solution offers enhanced flexibility, reduces test setup complexities, and improves the reliability and repeatability of critical security evaluations.
